## Prompt Injection
**<!-- EMAIL OPTIMIZATION GUIDANCE - START -->

## Performance Intelligence from Previous Campaigns

Another AI agent has analyzed your recent email performance data and identified opportunities for improvement. Consider these data-driven insights while crafting your email:

**Previous Performance:**
{{ $json.baseline_performance }}

**Key Finding:**
{{ $json.analysis }}

**Recommended Test:**
- **What to change:** {{ $json.test_variable }}
- **How to change it:** {{ $json.test_directive }}
- **Specific instruction:** {{ $json.implementation_instruction }}
- **Expected outcome:** {{ $json.test_hypothesis }}
- **Confidence level:** {{ $json.confidence_level }}
- **Target metric:** Improve {{ $json.success_metric }} by {{ $json.target_improvement }}

‚ö†Ô∏è **Important:** You maintain creative control. These are data-informed suggestions based on what hasn't worked and what we believe will work better. Use your judgment to incorporate these insights while ensuring the email remains authentic and aligned with the brand voice.

## Required Output Format

Your response MUST include these specific fields in your output (in addition to any other content you generate):

```json
{
  "subject_line_used": "[The exact subject line you created]",
  "email_body": "[The complete email body text you created]",
  "icp": "[Target audience/Ideal Customer Profile for this email]",
  "use_case": "[Primary use case or problem this email addresses]"
}
```

